# To-Do Web Application

## Overview

This project is a To-Do Web Application developed during the SkillCraft Technology Web Development Internship. The application helps users manage and organize daily tasks efficiently.

## Features

- Add tasks
- Edit tasks
- Delete tasks
- Mark tasks as completed
- Task organization
- Date and time management
- Responsive interface

## Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

## Project Structure

Task-04-ToDo-Web-App
│
├── index.html
├── style.css
├── script.js
└── assets

## How to Run

1. Download or clone repository
2. Open project folder
3. Run `index.html`

## Learning Outcomes

- CRUD operations
- DOM manipulation
- JavaScript event handling
- UI/UX design concepts

